        <item>
            <title>TGS 2023《人中之龍》攤位美女如雲   Kson、佐山愛現場面對觀眾 + 辣妹配鋼管舞</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/22/tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/22/tgs2023-sega-girls-girls-girls/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Long]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 09:46:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[《人中之龍 7 國際版》]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SEGA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[TGS 2023]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人中之龍]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1194821</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>TGS 東京電玩展 2023 貴為每年日本電玩盛事，往往都水洩不通。而 SEGA 官方攤位大有綽頭，非常識玩咁為觀眾準備鋼管舞表演以及大量美豔《人中之龍》夜總會小姐。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194842" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/37-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>TGS 2023 SEGA 今年攤位可謂非常吸引眼球，SEGA 攤位在開場階段，也為廣大玩家準備了鋼管舞表演，吸引了眾多人圍觀。更有美豔的《人中之龍》夜總會小姐輪流上場，令到現場試玩新作的隊伍需要排隊超過個半小時，要排到 100 分鐘之後。同時間為《人中之龍》主題的夜總會女孩拍照的遊客更加是絡繹不絕。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/39-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-1194841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="395" height="527" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-675x900.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/36-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 395px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/35-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1194848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/31-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而 SEGA 更加與去年一樣，包下了銀座一間 PUB ，舉辦了會後派對採用邀請制，主要入場包括貴賓、合作伙伴、媒體。現場除了商務合作對象外，更加多是日、韓的 KOL，設有享用飲品與食物招牌各位，亦邀請到了 DJ 演出 SEGA 旗下的各款遊戲音樂。派對重點就是幾位入選<span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">《人中之龍 7 外傳》選拔的公關小姐</span>，分別是知名日本實況主 Kson、公關小姐「<span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">あゆ」、寫真女星「</span><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1xmvt09 x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x xudqn12 x3x7a5m x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto">要あい」、AV 女優「佐山愛」、以及演員「中山こころ」，五位佳麗也盛裝出席，共同為 SEGA 宣傳。</span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
